    public interface RecordProcessor<I extends Record,O extends Record>
    A record processor performs some business logic on input records and produces output records. The output record may be of another type of the input record and will be piped out to the next processor if any.
    Author:
    Mahmoud Ben Hassine (mahmoud@benhassine.fr)
